MAGERA!

01:31.392 --> 01:34.393
[Magera Whispers]
Shhh...Quiet.

01:36.563 --> 01:38.464
[Cup Shatters]

01:58.751 --> 02:01.053
What has happened to you?

02:01.855 --> 02:03.222
Please no!

02:03.224 --> 02:08.961
[Screaming]

02:16.970 --> 02:21.406
[Hercules Screaming]

